=============================
=      File description     =
=============================
HumanSpaceShip.java - contains the human spaceship implementation 
RunnerSpaceShip.java - implements the runner space ship class.
SpaceShip.java- implements the spaceship father class.
SpaceShipAggressive.java- implements the aggressive spaceship.
SpaceShipBasher.java -implements the basher spaceship.
SpacShipDrunked.java- implements the drunked spaceship.
SpaceShipSpecial.java- implements the special spaceship.
SpaceShipFactory.java- implements the spaceship factory.
README




=============================
=          Design           =
=============================
I implemented the space ship class  as father class of all the other types of space ships.
i add additional 2 methods:
1)getsheild- true if sheild on false else
2)setCurrentEnergylevel-   add 1 to the energy level





=============================
=  Implementation details   =
=============================
all the different types of ships inherit from the space ship father class.
drunked space ship- * this ship act exactly the opposite from the humanspaceship
 * if the human press right it goes left.
 * shield is always on.
special space ship- special ship that act like the human but cant die.

